A London Mini Adventure 🇬🇧✨
Food, Boba, Blind Boxes, Gacha & a cheeky Pop Mart stop —🥰 aka joy in every corner!

🍴 Kicked things off with Char Siu Pork Bun heaven at JoyBao fluffy bao, rich flavour, and major comfort food vibes. Hidden gem alert in Nine Elms 😍

🧋 Then it was bubble tea + a Sonny Angel blind box 👼 from BOBA on Shaftesbury Ave because drinks taste better with a tiny surprise.

🎰 Next up: Gacha heaven at Kissaten | Fuyu — Japanese treats + capsule toy magic = pure serotonin.

🛍️ Finished with a cheeky stop at Pop Mart on Oxford Street 💛 yes, more blind boxes… no regrets.

📍 JoyBao
Unit 20B, 15-17 Ingate Pl, Nine Elms, London SW8 3NS

📍 BOBA
55-57 Shaftesbury Ave, London W1D 6LD

📍 Kissaten | Fuyu
72 Old Compton St, London W1D 4UN

📍 Pop Mart
262 Oxford St, London W1C 1DW

A wholesome day of treats, toys, and tiny joys ✨ Save this for your next London wander!

Workwear With Joy 🐆 
Yesterday was chilly and grey, and I almost threw on a plain black raincoat… but instead, I reached for this leopard-print Ganni x Barbour @ganni @barbour jacket to add a little joy to the day. Sometimes all it takes is one bold piece to shift your whole mood ✨ ☁️ 

#WorkwearWithJoy #WhatMarieWears #JoyfulDressing #StatementOuterwear #GanniXBarbour #RainyDayStyle #StyleOver40

Back to work after half term and straight into teaching P.E. so all the energy was very much needed! 💥

Wearing head-to-toe @adanola and honestly, I’m obsessed. I had my eye on this ‘Mesh Short Sleeve Sports Jersey’ for weeks and was so excited when it came back in stock! 🙌

And the leggings? Now I totally get the hype. Super comfy, supportive, and perfect for a full day of teaching on my feet.

Jersey, leggings and socks @adanola 

#adanola #adanolastyle #PEteacherstyle #workwearbutmakeitactive #teacherootd #comfortandstyle #workwearwithjoy

Whenever I post a pic of my roses and peonies, I always get the loveliest messages especially from my Portuguese aunties (thanks Tias) 🤭💌 I’m often asked how I look after them, and honestly? The secret is simple, lots of love, attention, and a little bit of talking to them too 🤣🤣🤣🌹✨🌸
I grow David Austin roses, which honestly do half the work by just being breathtaking. The rest is care… and a little sweet-talking.
